Package org.jcvlib.io

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    VideoReader
    Interface for reading stream of images from different sources (from web-cameras, video file, network and etc.).
    VideoWriter
    Interface for writing images to video stream of different sources (video file, network and etc.).
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ImageRW
    Class for Input/Output images.
    VideoFileReader
    This class allow read video from disk.
    VideoFileWriter
    This class allow write video to disk.
    WebCamReader
    This class allow get images from web-cameras.
